div.h3: Abstract Syntax Tree Structure & Operator Precedence

g.text: Operator Precedence: AND Binds Tighter Than OR

div.p: Tree Depth = Evaluation Order Deeper nodes are evaluated first (bottom-up).

ul.li: In a OR b AND c: AND is deeper evaluated first
In (a OR b) AND c: OR is deeper evaluated first Parentheses force a "fresh parse" at the lowest precedence, effectively restarting the tree construction.

g.text: produces different trees for same tokens
